LINKED LIST

It is a linear list in which there is a logical order of the elements, that is, the order viewed by the user has the same physical order (in main memory).

1) Modeling
Modeling is done using an array of records.
These records contain information of interest to the user.
The arrangement will have a fixed size and the number of elements is controlled with an additional variable.

2) Management functions
initialize the structure
return the number of valid elements
display the elements of the structure
search for an element in the structure
insert elements into the structure
delete elements in the structure
reinitialize the structure
